---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Getting Started" showSearch={false}>
  <div class="container page-content">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1>Getting Started with nex</h1>
      <p class="lead">Your journey to better tool management starts here.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Installation</h2>
      <p>Install nex on your system using one of the following methods:</p>
      
      <div class="install-options">
        <div class="install-card">
          <h3>Windows</h3>
          <p>Download the installer or run via PowerShell:</p>
          <pre><code>iwr https://github.com/devkiraa/nex/releases/latest/download/install.ps1 -useb | iex</code></pre>
        </div>
        
        <div class="install-card">
          <h3>Linux / macOS</h3>
          <p>Run the installation script:</p>
          <pre><code>curl -fsSL https://github.com/devkiraa/nex/releases/latest/download/install.sh | sh</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>First Steps</h2>
      <p>Once installed, verify the installation by checking the version:</p>
      <pre><code>nex --version</code></pre>

      <h3>Installing a Package</h3>
      <p>Try installing a package, for example, the <code>hello-world</code> package:</p>
      <pre><code>nex install hello-world</code></pre>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Quick Examples</h2>
      <p>Here are some common commands to get you moving:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><code>nex search &lt;query&gt;</code> - Search for packages</li>
        <li><code>nex list</code> - List installed packages</li>
        <li><code>nex update &lt;package&gt;</code> - Update a package</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-content {
    padding-top: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  
  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--nex-black);
  }
  
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--nex-gray);
  }
  
  .section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    background: var(--nex-white);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    border: 1px solid var(--nex-border);
  }
  
  .section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--nex-red);
    display: inline-block;
  }
  
  .section h3 {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .install-options {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .install-options {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }
  
  .install-card {
    background: var(--nex-bg);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border: 1px solid var(--nex-border);
  }
  
  ul {
    list-style-position: inside;
    margin-left: 1rem;
  }
  
  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
